snippet.textDisplay:
Tu Kuja Man Kuja is Persian, that is Farsi, for the next line, Tu kahaan, main kahaan. Tu is tu, you. Man is main, I. And Kuja is kahaan, where.

Hence, Tu Kuja man kuja means 'where are you, where am I', or 'tu kahaan, main kahaan' 

Like if you was trying to thinking of meaning this ... Love You Muhammad SAW 
Pakistan Zindabad
